title: Our Favorite Underrated YouTube Channels, Mechanical Keyboards, & Tech Embargoes Explained
description:
This week, Marques and Andrew recommend a few of their favorite lesser-known YouTube channels, look at the world of Mechanical Keyboards and how much we still need to learn about them, and take the "Explained!" series to the podcast to explain how embargoes work and how they affect content creators. Plus, some fun behind the scenes stories before we wrap it all up with our regularly-scheduled Listener Q & A!
